datasets.name: aed0df20
queryLines:
WITH growth AS (
  SELECT
    STNAME,
    CTYNAME,
    Location,
    PREDICTEDPOP2027,
    Predicted_AGI2027,
    AGI_per_capita_2027,
    Pop_Diff_2022_to_2027 AS Pop_Growth,
    Pop_PercChange_2022_to_2027 AS Pop_Growth_Perc,
    AGI_Diff_2022_to_2027 AS AGI_Growth,
    AGI_PercChange_2022_to_2027 AS AGI_Growth_Perc
  FROM ets_thriventcohort.default.county_population_agi
  WHERE Pop_Diff_2022_to_2027 > 0 AND AGI_Diff_2022_to_2027 > 0 and PREDICTEDPOP2027 > 250000 and AGI_per_capita_2027 > 40 and AGI2022 > 15000000
),

ranked AS (
  SELECT *,
    RANK() OVER (ORDER BY Pop_Growth_Perc DESC) AS Pop_Rank,
    RANK() OVER (ORDER BY AGI_Growth_Perc DESC) AS AGI_Rank
  FROM growth
)

SELECT *,
  (Pop_Rank + AGI_Rank) AS Composite_Score
FROM ranked
ORDER BY Composite_Score ASC
limit 50

datasets.name: 855dbe93
queryLines:
WITH growth AS (
  SELECT
    Location,
    AGI_2027_predicted,
    pop_2027_predicted,
    AGI_per_capita_2027,
    pop_change_raw AS Pop_Growth,
    pop_change_pct AS Pop_Growth_Perc,
    AGI_change_raw AS AGI_Growth,
    AGI_change_pct AS AGI_Growth_Perc
  FROM ets_thriventcohort.default.county_forecast_combined
  WHERE pop_change_raw > 0 AND AGI_change_raw > 0 and pop_2027_predicted > 250000 and AGI_2027_predicted > 20000000 and AGI_per_capita_2027 > 50 AND Location NOT LIKE '%Minnesota%'
),

ranked AS (
  SELECT *,
    RANK() OVER (ORDER BY Pop_Growth_Perc DESC) AS Pop_Rank,
    RANK() OVER (ORDER BY AGI_Growth_Perc DESC) AS AGI_Rank
  FROM growth
)

SELECT *,
  (Pop_Rank + AGI_Rank) AS Composite_Score
FROM ranked
ORDER BY Composite_Score ASC

frame.title: Composite Score
frame.description: Composite Score is the rank of each each county in population growth and AGI growth combined. (Lower is better)
Size of the bubble is AGI per Capita
